maxpower.kernel
Class TreeReduce

java.lang.Object
  maxpower.kernel.TreeReduce

public class TreeReduce
extends java.lang.Object

A set of static methods to perform a reduction in a tree-like manner. Tree reduction incurs less scheduling resource cost than a naive reduction and the operations are performed with lower latency. Naive reduction Tree reduction a b c d a b c d \ / | | \ / \ / x | | x x \ / | \ / x | x \ / x NB. For operations which are not strictly associative (e.g. floating-point addition), using tree reduction may affect the result slightly as the order of operations is altered.
